==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Meliphagan
<hw>Me*liph"a*gan</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Any bird
of the genus <gen>Meliphaga</gen> and allied genera; a honey eater; --
called also <altname>meliphagidan</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Meliphagous</ent>⟦br⟧
